      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 09:23:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>盈利和经济不确定性导致欧洲股市继续下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/european-stocks-pull-back-again-after-best-day-since-november</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于好坏参半的盈利报告和不确定的美国经济前景给市场人气带来压力，欧洲股市重新开始下滑，结束了连续两天的反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/european-stocks-pull-back-again-after-best-day-since-november</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 07:21:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
